1- Exit the house
2- Go to bus station and wait for it
   If bus is arrived get in the bus else wait for it to be arrive
3- Get in the bus 
   While you are inside the bus stay in bus to reach the destination stop
4- Get off the bus in destination bus stop
   If bus arrived to destination go to school
5- If school is open, enter the school
   Else wait for it until it opened
   When it opened enter to school

